- **Plugin Manifests**: `/extensions/{plugin-id}/openclaw.plugin.json`
- **Entry Points**: `/extensions/{plugin-id}/index.ts`, `/extensions/{plugin-id}/setup-entry.ts`
- **Entry Type Definitions**: `/src/plugin-sdk/plugin-entry.ts`, `/src/plugin-sdk/core.ts`, `/src/plugin-sdk/provider-entry.ts`
- **Plugin Type System**: `/src/plugins/types.ts`
- **SDK Registry**: `/scripts/lib/plugin-sdk-entrypoints.json`
- **Manifest Documentation**: `/docs/plugins/manifest.md`
- **SDK Documentation**: `/docs/plugins/sdk-*.md`

